cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.SY, cs.NE 

The paper discusses an optimization method for machine learning and reinforcement learning problems, specifically for policy evaluation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions linear function approximation, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of gradient estimates and optimization methods also suggests the categories of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the mention of reinforcement learning implies the category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
